292
00:17:39,748 --> 00:17:41,848
In other words,

293
00:17:41,848 --> 00:17:47,848
Mr. Kagazume drank from the tumbler he poisoned himself.

294
00:17:47,848 --> 00:17:50,148
What? Could it be...

