00:18:24,148 --> 00:18:26,748
then to break into the law office and steal it.

307
00:18:26,748 --> 00:18:29,548
"Will and Testament" -And this is his written confession.

308
00:18:29,548 --> 00:18:31,048
What?

309
00:18:31,048 --> 00:18:35,448
They wrote articles

310
00:18:35,448 --> 00:18:38,348
mocking the people they enraged.

311
00:18:38,348 --> 00:18:42,748
But after the attempted murder,

312
00:18:42,748 --> 00:18:46,648
