318
00:19:03,948 --> 00:19:08,748
Rejecting the idea and fearing the truth would come to light,

319
00:19:08,748 --> 00:19:12,248
Mr. Hashizume plotted to kill Mr. Kagazume,

320
00:19:12,248 --> 00:19:18,048
without realizing Mr. Kagazume had made his own plans

321
00:19:18,048 --> 00:19:20,348
to kill Mr. Hashizume.

322
00:19:20,348 --> 00:19:22,648
Mr. Hashizume and Mr. Kagazume.

323
00:19:22,648 --> 00:19:24,848
The murderous intent you felt

