00:19:37,748 --> 00:19:40,148
This is the last time! You'd better not regret it!

330
00:19:40,148 --> 00:19:42,248
Enough already, you hypocrite!

331
00:19:59,048 --> 00:20:04,948
Mr. Kagazume realized you deliberately took his tumbler,

332
00:20:04,948 --> 00:20:09,848
